('Blowers & Mulchers', 'TRIVAC W/ MULTI-STAGE ALL METAL MULCHING SYSTEM (WG509)', 'All-in-one design: leaf blower, mulcher & vacuum. Quickly converts from leaf blower to vacuum mode with the flip of a switch. Two-stage metal impeller with shredder blade provides an 18:1 mulch ratio. Electronic variable speed control for corners and heavy debris. Quick-release button makes cleaning debris as easy as ever', 119.99, 'ITEM WG509'),
('Blowers & Mulchers', 'TURBINEFUSION LEAF BLOWER, MULCHER & VACUUM', 'Patented all-in-one single tube system: blower, mulcher & yard vacuum. TURBINE fan technology delivers forceful, high-capacity air volume. Instantly converts from blower to vac with the flip of a switch. Dual-stage metal impeller provides 24:1 mulch ratio. 2-Speed control lets you adjust for light or heavy-duty jobs. Dynamic airflow design for maximum performance', 89.99, 'ITEM WG510'),
('Blowers & Mulchers', 'AIR CORDLESS LEAF BLOWER / SWEEPER HI-CAPACITY (4.0 AH)', 'Double the Run Time with the new 4.0Ah Hi-Capacity Battery System. Cordless convenience to quickly clean up your deck, driveway, sidewalk, patio & all around your house. Lightweight, compact design: easy to use and easy to store. Includes 8 attachments for a variety of cleaning tasks. Ultra-fast clean up without having to move a single thing. 120 mph air speed with 80 cfm air flow, and only 4.3 lbs. Bonus Deflator Attachment - easily deflate rafts, pool toys & mattresses', 119.97, 'ITEM WG545.4'),
('Blowers & Mulchers', 'GT REVOLUTION 20V STRING TRIMMER & BLOWER COMBO KIT', 'WORX unites the ultimate in grass trimming and turbine blower technology. New! GT REVOLUTION. Patented Command Feed™ Technology automatically extends fresh line, as you need it. Don''t stop. Just press and trim. A Full Foot Longer than the original WORX GT. Plus extreme versatility with 7 different handle and 6 different rotating head positions. Less Downtime with the new extra spool holder on board. Just snap in an extra spool before leaving the garage. TURBINE20V™ TURBINE fan technology delivers forceful, high-capacity air volume. 2-Speed control to quickly switch between lighter & tougher jobs. Hyper-Stream air nozzle focuses air flow for extra tough conditions.', 149.94, 'ITEM WG954'),
('Blowers & Mulchers - Cordless', '20V AIR CORDLESS LEAF BLOWER / SWEEPER', 'Cordless battery powered leaf blower convenience lets you quickly and easily clean your deck, driveway, sidewalk, patio & more — maintain all around your home. Lightweight, small cordless leaf blower design that''s easy to use and easy to store — weighs less than 4 lbs. 120 mph air speed provides enough power to clean large areas. Includes 8 leaf blower attachments for a variety of cleaning tasks including hard-to-reach spaces. Bonus Deflator Attachment - easily deflate rafts, pool toys & mattresses. Part of the 20V Power Share platform so you can share rechargeable leaf blower batteries with other WORX products', 99.99, 'ITEM WG545.1'),
('Blowers & Mulchers - Cordless', '56V STRING TRIMMER & TURBINE LEAF BLOWER COMBO KIT', 'Two powerful 56V MaxLithium batteries provides gas-like performance & extended run time with zero emissions. String trimmer converts to a wheeled edger in just seconds. Command Feed line length advancement provides line when needed with the touch of a button. TURBINE fan technology delivers forceful, high-capacity air volume. Highly efficient Brushless Motor for long lasting power', 349.99, 'ITEM WG926'),
('Blowers & Mulchers - Electric', 'TURBINE450 ELECTRIC LEAF BLOWER', 'High capacity air volume with turbine fan technology. 2-speed control for versatility (360-450cfm). Hyper-stream air nozzle for extra tough conditions. Dynamic airflow design for maximum performance. Lightweight and ergonomic one-hand operation. Cord retainer for hassle free leaf blowing. Simple tool free assembly', 37.99, 'ITEM WG519'),
('Blowers & Mulchers - Electric', 'TURBINE600 ELECTRIC LEAF BLOWER', 'TURBINE fan technology delivers forceful, high-capacity air volume. Up to twice as fast as professional gas blowers. Variable speed control to quickly clean up your outdoor spaces. Dynamic airflow design for maximum performance. Features a Hyper-Stream air nozzle for extra tough conditions. Cord retainer for hassle-free leaf blowing', 59.99, 'ITEM WG520'),
('Blowers & Mulchers - Accessories', 'LEAFPRO UNIVERSAL COLLECTION SYSTEM WITH TURBINE ADAPTER', 'Universal: fits all major blower/vac brands - gas and electric. Designed for no touch, high-capacity leaf collection. High-flow, ventilated mesh hood adjusts to fit 32-96 gallon round or square trash cans. Flexible, industrial strength 8-foot hose with up to 16-feet of surrounding reach. Includes adapter to fit TURBINE Fusion Leaf Blower, Mulcher & Vacuum', 49.99, 'ITEM WA4057'),
('Blowers & Mulchers - Accessories', 'TURBINE FUSION REPLACEMENT BAG', 'Easy-empty collection bag with capacity of up to .85 bushels. Compatible with the WG510', 29.99, 'ITEM 50030182'),

