('Turbine Leaf Blowers', '40V GT 3.0 TRIMMER & TURBINE BLOWER COMBO KIT', '40V Li-ion Cordless 2-pc Combo Kit includes WG180 and WG580 with 2 batteries. 12" 40-Volt Li-ion Cordless Grass Trimmer/Edger w/ (2) 40V Li-ion batteries for longer run time. Telescopic shaft adjusts to user’s height and posture for quick adjustments in the yard. The rubberized twin wheel set supports and guides the edger for straight cuts. Innovative Command Feed™ spool system for instant line feeding. High capacity air volume with turbine fan technology (340 CFM). Hyper-stream air nozzle for extra tough conditions', 149.99, 'ITEM WG925'),
('Turbine Leaf Blowers', 'GT REVOLUTION 20V 12" STRING TRIMMER / EDGER / MINI-MOWER', 'New GT Revolution is changing the world, one yard at a time. Patented Command Feed™ Technology automatically extends fresh line, as you need it. Don''t stop. Just press and trim. 3-in-1 Flexibility from precision string trimmer...to powerful in-line wheeled edger...to easy-to-navigate mini mower. A Full Foot Longer than the original WORX GT. Extreme versatility with 7 handle and 6 rotating head positions. Less Downtime with new extra spool holder on board. Plus Free Spools for Life. Two 20V Power Share Batteries Included so you can always be running and charging', 99.96, 'ITEM WG170'),
('Turbine Leaf Blowers', 'GT REVOLUTION 20V 4.0AH STRING TRIMMER & BLOWER COMBO KIT', 'Patented Command Feed™ Technology automatically extends fresh line, as you need it. Don''t stop. Just press and trim. A Full Foot Longer than the original WORX GT. Plus extreme versatility with 7 different handle and 6 different rotating head positions. Less Downtime with the new extra spool holder on board. Just snap in an extra spool before leaving the garage. TURBINE20V™ TURBINE fan technology delivers forceful, high-capacity air volume. 2-Speed control to quickly switch between lighter & tougher jobs. Hyper-Stream air nozzle focuses air flow for extra tough conditions.', 199.98, 'ITEM WG954.1'),
('Turbine Leaf Blowers - Cordless', '2X20V 13" CORDLESS STRING TRIMMER & WHEELED EDGER - TOOL ONLY', 'Product uses two 20V Power Share batteries to deliver 40V Power and Performance. Innovative Command Feed™ spool system for instant line feeding at the click of a button. Variable speed throttle control extends run time and provides power for various grass conditions. Pivoting cutting head and straight shaft design can tackle any terrain. With various ways to adjust the trimmer to any job, this trimmer/edger can easily manage any home-site up to a 1/2 acre. Being a part of the 20V Power Share program allows endless possibilities to share batteries with many other tools. *Battery & Charger Not Included', 99.99, 'ITEM WG184.9'),
('Turbine Leaf Blowers - Cordless', '20V 12" GT 3.0 STRING TRIMMER & WHEELED EDGER', 'Converts from a string trimmer to a wheeled edger in just seconds. Innovative Command Feed spool system for instant line feeding & Free Spools for Life. Features 3 powerful and lightweight MaxLithium batteries, as well as a 2hr dual charger. Rubberized twin wheel set supports and guides the edger', 149.99, 'ITEM WG163.4'),
('Turbine Leaf Blowers - Electric', '6 AMP ELECTRIC 15" STRING TRIMMER & EDGER', 'The WORX WG124 2-in1 Trimmer is designed for maximum performance. The 6 Amp electric grass trimmer incorporates a telescoping shaft and multi-position adjustable head for additional comfort. Quickly rotate the handle and adjust the head for a fully functioning in-line wheeled edger that professional clean lawn edge. A foldable spacer guard prevents the cutting edge from damaging trees, furniture, walls or delicate landscaping. It also features a dual auto-feed trimmer line system, so you''ll never have to bump the trimmer to feed additional line. The auto-feed ensures you have the perfect amount of line at all times.', 49.99, 'ITEM WG124'),
('Turbine Leaf Blowers - Electric', '12 AMP ELECTRIC 7.5" LAWN EDGER / TRENCHER', 'Powerful 12 Amp motor provides professional, clean cut edges. 3-position blade depth adjustment for various applications. Cutting line indicator for optimal precision. Adjustable shaft to accommodate height and posture', 89.99, 'ITEM WG896'),
('Turbine Leaf Blowers - Accessories', 'FREE SPOOLS FOR LIFE 6-PACK', 'DNA2 DoubleHelix cutting line for superior trimming & edging performance. Spools come pre-wound and are replaced easily in just seconds. Each package contains 6 spools (60 feet) of DNA2 trimmer line. Simply pay the cost of Shipping & Processing: $8.62/package of 6', 0.00, 'ITEM WA0010'),
('Turbine Leaf Blowers - Accessories', '20V & 18V MAXLITHIUM BATTERY 25-MINUTE QUICK CHARGER', 'Quickly charge your 20V or 18V battery in just 25 minutes to reduce downtime between charges. Features a built-in charge indicator for easy use. Long cord provides flexibility to charge your battery in various locations. May be mounted to your wall for compact storage', 49.99, 'ITEM WA3835'),
('Turbine Leaf Blowers - Cordless', '20V 12" CORDLESS STRING TRIMMER & EDGER', 'Converts from a string trimmer to an edger in just seconds. Adjustable cutting width from 10"-12" for a wider cutting path or extended run time. Features a powerful and lightweight MaxLithium 20V battery. Foldable spacer guard helps protect flowers and lawn ornaments. 100% Automatic single line feed for optimal cutting performance', 69.99, 'ITEM WG154'),

