('Power Tools - Work Support', 'CLAMPING SAWHORSES WITH BAR CLAMPS', 'Included bar clamps attach without tools and may be used with or without the sawhorses. Lightweight and easy to transport wherever they are needed. Accommodates both horizontal and vertical clamping positions. Features a built-in shelf and cord hooks for storing tools, cords and other materials', 69.00, 'ITEM WX065'),
('Power Tools', 'AI DRILL 20V DRILL & DRIVER IN ONE ', 'Automated BITLOCK™ tightens around the bit, 30% more holding force than hand-tightening chuck. SAFEDRIVE stops driven screw flush with work surface, prevents damage to work and screw. PULSE ASSIST prevents bit from slipping when drilling hard surfaces, or driving or removing soft or worn screws', 119.85, 'ITEM WX178L'),
('Power Tools', '4V CORDLESS XTD XTENDED REACH DRIVER', 'Patented extending shaft reaches into recessed areas. Longer shaft improves control and helps drive screws straighter. Offset chuck provides access in tight corners. Powerful 4V MaxLithium battery holds a charge for up to 18 months', 34.99, 'ITEM WX252L'),
('Power Tools - Work Support', 'PEGASUS FOLDING WORK TABLE & SAWHORSE', 'Versatile folding work table that may be used as a sawhorse and portable workbench. Integrated clamping system holds materials firmly in place. Collapsible workbench design and lightweight for easy transportation & storage. Includes 2 bar clamps and 4 clamp dogs', 119.99, 'ITEM WX051'),
('Power Tools - Work Support', 'JAWHORSE PORTABLE CLAMPING WORK SUPPORT STATION ', 'Multi-purpose, heavy duty workstation with powerful clamping up to 1,000kg (2200lbs). Flexible clamping capacity holding 1mm to 880 mm (34.6 in). Hands free locking – no assistance needed with foot operation clamping. Solid heavy duty steel construction holds up to 440lbs', 99.99, 'ITEM WX060.2'),
('Power Tools - Drills & Drivers', '20V BRUSHLESS DRILL & DRIVER - TOOL ONLY', 'Brushless motor maximizes efficiency for more power and longer run time. PulseAssist improves screwdriving bit control to prevent stripping screws and helps loosen stubborn screws. PulseAssist reduces the likelihood of a drill bit tip "walking" when starting a hole on hard surfaces. Compact and easy to control; excellent power to weight ratio. 2-speed gearbox provides 0-430/0-1600 rpm. 354 in lbs maximum torque *Battery & Charger sold separately', 79.99, 'ITEM WX174L.9'),
('Power Tools - Drills & Drivers', '8V CORDLESS IMPACT FORCEDRIVER', 'Excellent for driving large fasteners and removing seized or rusted bolts. 3-position handle adjusts for best approach to work piece. LED light illuminates the work area. 1800 rpm; 3000 ipm Includes #2 phillips driving bit and 5-hour charger. Maximum torque 225 in-lbs.', 39.99, 'ITEM WX270L'),
('Power Tools - Saws', 'EXACTRACK 20V 6-1/2" CIRCULAR SAW', 'Circular saws just became easier with the new ExacTrack™ Circular Saw. ExacTrack™ is an innovative function, which can help to make a straight cut easier by keeping the blade flush against the cutting guide board. In standard mode, the saw will be set up for regular 90-degree or bevel cutting. WORX Power Share tools lets you tackle every job with our 20V Max Battery. Simply swap out tools with a click, and you''re on to the next project.', 119.99, 'ITEM WX530L'),
('Power Tools - Saws', '20V AXIS CORDLESS RECIPROCATING & JIG SAW', 'Pivoting head design converts from a reciprocating saw to a jig saw in seconds. Powerful 20V MaxLithium battery delivers long-lasting performance. Orbital cutting technology provides a more efficient cut. Compatible with standard reciprocating saw and t-shank jig saw blades. Built-in blower removes dust and debris to increase cutting visibility. Compact & lightweight for easy use', 119.00, 'ITEM WX550L.1'),
('Power Tools - Oscillating Tools', '3.0 AMP OSCILLATING TOOL WITH 9 ACCESSORIES', 'Multi-function oscillating tool for sanding, sawing, scraping, shaping, polishing and removing grout. Universal Fit System accepts all other brand’s accessories. 3 amp; 11,000 - 21,000opm; 2.9 lbs w/o cord. Includes allen hex key for loosening blade holding screw. Oscillating Multitool with Universal Fit System and including end cut blade, rigid scraper, sanding pad, and 6 sanding sheets.', 69.99, 'ITEM WX668L'),
('Power Tools - Oscillating Tools', '2.5 AMP OSCILLATING MULTI-TOOL', 'Powerful 2.5 Amp motor for detailed or heavy duty jobs. Universal Fit System accepts all other brand’s accessories. Provides multiple functions that include cutting, sawing, sanding, scraping, polishing, shaping and grout removal. Variable speed dial for precision control', 59.99, 'ITEM WX665L'),
('Power Tools - Accessories', '16-PIECE DRILL & DRIVE BIT SET', '1/4" hex shank for quick bit changes. Durable HSS bits for metal, wood, plastic and aluminum. 135-degree split points for precision drilling. Features a locking storage case for convenience and easy transportation. Works great with the WORX Switchdriver 2-in-1 Cordless Drill & Driver', 19.99, 'ITEM WA1112'),
('Power Tools - Accessories', 'BLADERUNNER 10 PC T-SHANK BLADE ASSORTMENT', 'Jigsaw assorted blade set, sold as 10 blades per pack. T-Shank blades fit Worx BladeRunner (WX572L) 21TPI BIM Metal cutting blade*2 8TPI HSS Aluminum cutting blade*2 50# 65Mn Ceramics blade*2 10TPI HCS Wood cutting smooth blade*2 6TPI HCS Wood cutting scroll blade*2 Blades come fitted in plastic case', 29.99, 'ITEM WA8006'),

